  "ps3.8:7.6": "nirāmisaṃ sukhaṃ vedanaṃ …",
  "ps3.8:7.7": "sāmisaṃ dukkhaṃ vedanaṃ …",
  "ps3.8:7.8": "nirāmisaṃ dukkhaṃ vedanaṃ …",
  "ps3.8:7.9": "sāmisaṃ adukkhamasukhaṃ vedanaṃ …",
  "ps3.8:7.10": "nirāmisaṃ adukkhamasukhaṃ vedanaṃ …",
  "ps3.8:7.11": "cakkhusamphassajaṃ vedanaṃ …",
