  "ps3.8:7.15": "kāyasamphassajaṃ vedanaṃ …",
  "ps3.8:7.16": "manosamphassajaṃ vedanaṃ aniccato anupassati, no niccato …pe…",
  "ps3.8:7.17": "paṭinissajjati, no ādiyati.",
  "ps3.8:7.18": "Aniccato anupassanto niccasaññaṃ pajahati …pe…",
  "ps3.8:7.19": "paṭinissajjanto ādānaṃ pajahati.",
  "ps3.8:7.20": "Imehi sattahi ākārehi vedanaṃ anupassati.",
  "ps3.8:7.21": "Vedanā upaṭṭhānaṃ, no sati.",
  "ps3.8:7.22": "Sati upaṭṭhānañceva sati ca.",
  "ps3.8:7.23": "Tāya satiyā tena ñāṇena taṃ vedanaṃ anupassati.",
  "ps3.8:7.24": "Tena vuccati—",
  "ps3.8:7.25": "“vedanāsu vedanānupassanāsatipaṭṭhānā”.",
  "ps3.8:8.1": "**Bhāvanā**ti catasso bhāvanā …pe…",
  "ps3.8:8.2": "evaṃ vedanāsu vedanānupassī viharati. (2)",
  "ps3.8:9.1": "Kathaṃ **citte cittānupassī viharati?**",
  "ps3.8:9.2": "Idhekacco sarāgaṃ cittaṃ aniccato anupassati, no niccato …pe…",
  "ps3.8:9.3": "paṭinissajjati, no ādiyati.",
  "ps3.8:9.4": "Aniccato anupassanto niccasaññaṃ pajahati …pe…",
  "ps3.8:9.5": "paṭinissajjanto ādānaṃ pajahati.",
  "ps3.8:9.6": "Imehi sattahi ākārehi cittaṃ anupassati.",
  "ps3.8:9.7": "Cittaṃ upaṭṭhānaṃ, no sati.",
  "ps3.8:9.8": "Sati upaṭṭhānañceva sati ca.",
  "ps3.8:9.9": "Tāya satiyā tena ñāṇena taṃ cittaṃ anupassati.",
  "ps3.8:9.10": "Tena vuccati—",
  "ps3.8:9.11": "“citte cittānupassanāsatipaṭṭhānā”.",
  "ps3.8:10.1": "**Bhāvanā**ti catasso bhāvanā …pe…",
  "ps3.8:10.2": "āsevanaṭṭhena bhāvanā.",
  "ps3.8:11.1": "Idhekacco vītarāgaṃ cittaṃ …pe…",
  "ps3.8:11.2": "sadosaṃ cittaṃ …",
