  "ps3.8:11.23": "Aniccato anupassanto niccasaññaṃ pajahati …pe…",
  "ps3.8:11.24": "paṭinissajjanto ādānaṃ pajahati.",
  "ps3.8:11.25": "Imehi sattahi ākārehi cittaṃ anupassati.",
  "ps3.8:11.26": "Cittaṃ upaṭṭhānaṃ, no sati.",
  "ps3.8:11.27": "Sati upaṭṭhānañceva sati ca.",
  "ps3.8:11.28": "Tāya satiyā tena ñāṇena taṃ cittaṃ anupassati.",
  "ps3.8:11.29": "Tena vuccati—",
  "ps3.8:11.30": "“citte cittānupassanāsatipaṭṭhānā”.",
  "ps3.8:12.1": "**Bhāvanā**ti catasso bhāvanā …pe…",
  "ps3.8:12.2": "āsevanaṭṭhena bhāvanā.",
  "ps3.8:12.3": "Evaṃ citte cittānupassī viharati. (3)",
  "ps3.8:13.1": "Kathaṃ **dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati?**",
  "ps3.8:13.2": "Idhekacco ṭhapetvā kāyaṃ ṭhapetvā vedanaṃ ṭhapetvā cittaṃ tadavasese dhamme aniccato anupassati, no niccato;",
  "ps3.8:13.3": "dukkhato anupassati, no sukhato;",
  "ps3.8:13.4": "anattato anupassati, no attato;",
  "ps3.8:13.5": "nibbindati, no nandati;",
  "ps3.8:13.6": "virajjati, no rajjati;",
  "ps3.8:13.7": "nirodheti, no samudeti;",
  "ps3.8:13.8": "paṭinissajjati, no ādiyati.",
  "ps3.8:13.9": "Aniccato anupassanto niccasaññaṃ pajahati, dukkhato anupassanto sukhasaññaṃ pajahati, anattato anupassanto attasaññaṃ pajahati, nibbindanto nandiṃ pajahati, virajjanto rāgaṃ pajahati, nirodhento samudayaṃ pajahati, paṭinissajjanto ādānaṃ pajahati.",
  "ps3.8:13.10": "Imehi sattahi ākārehi te dhamme anupassati.",
  "ps3.8:13.11": "Dhammā upaṭṭhānaṃ, no sati.",
  "ps3.8:13.12": "Sati upaṭṭhānañceva sati ca.",
  "ps3.8:13.13": "Tāya satiyā tena ñāṇena te dhamme anupassati.",
  "ps3.8:13.14": "Tena vuccati—",
  "ps3.8:13.15": "“dhammesu dhammānupassanāsatipaṭṭhānā”.",
  "ps3.8:14.1": "**Bhāvanā**ti catasso bhāvanā—",
  "ps3.8:14.2": "tattha jātānaṃ dhammānaṃ anativattanaṭṭhena bhāvanā, indriyānaṃ ekarasaṭṭhena bhāvanā, tadupagavīriyavāhanaṭṭhena bhāvanā, āsevanaṭṭhena bhāvanā.",
  "ps3.8:14.3": "Evaṃ dhammesu dhammānupassī viharatīti. (4)",
  "ps3.8:14.4": "Satipaṭṭhānakathā niṭṭhitā."
}